This film is terrible. It has none of the intrigue of Legion and none of the cool scenes of Paranormal Activity. It's a drawn out boring film that never pays off. The ending is terrible and insults an already tired viewer. A lot of hype surrounded this film, kind of like The Fourth Kind, but it's actually worse than that hunk of crap. Waste of time. Watch it if you want, but don't say that you were not warned.

Thanks for the upload. I do appreciate being able to watch it and the quality of the video has nothing to do with my review. The torrent is fine. I blame the film makers for making this horrible movie.
